law.text: Each professional service corporation shall file an annual report as provided in KRS 14A.6-010. A duplicate original copy of each annual report shall be filed with the regulating board which licenses the shareholders of the corporation.
law.history: Amended 2010 Ky. Acts ch. 151, sec. 70, effective January 1, 2011. -- Amended 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 288, sec. 13, effective July 15, 1980. -- Amended 1972 Ky. Acts ch. 274, sec. 155. -- Created 1962 Ky. Acts ch. 236, sec. 11.
